 (254,1,'2013-12-20 01:41:15','2013-12-20 01:41:15','最值得群硕人期待的年度庆典即将拉启！2013/12/27，上海率先启动，2014/1/10，武汉接力庆典热潮！\n\n本次年度庆典，将以“群硕好声音”为主题。自12/2筹备起，马上掀起热潮，短短几天就有200多首各式风格的歌曲登陆投票平台。经过大众和专家评选，上海武汉将各有10名选手踏上年度庆典。谁将是群硕好声音达人呢，将由群硕好耳朵的小伙伴们决定哦，那一刻，小伙伴们，请通过微信为好声音投票欢呼啦!\n\n年度庆典除了“好声音”外，当然还有大餐、大礼及缤纷多彩的特邀节目奉上~让我们一起期待属于群硕人的大party，让我们一起期待2014年的精彩\n','2014 群硕Annual Party','','inherit','closed','open','','300200-%e7%bc%a9%e7%95%a5%e5%9b%be','','','2013-12-20 01:41:15','2013-12-20 01:41:15','',167,'http://192.168.222.177:8011//wp-content/uploads/2013/09/300200-缩略图.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),
 (176,1,'2013-09-12 02:04:38','2013-09-12 02:04:38','<a href=\"http://192.168.222.119/recruitingcms/exciting-activities/campus-basketball/\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-157 aligncenter\" alt=\"1_564x234\" src=\"http://localhost/recruitingcms/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/1_564x234-300x124.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"124\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://192.168.222.119/recruitingcms/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2_564x234.png\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-158 aligncenter\" alt=\"2_564x234\" src=\"http://localhost/recruitingcms/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2_564x234-300x124.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"124\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://192.168.222.119/recruitingcms/exciting-activities/moo-release/\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-159 aligncenter\" alt=\"3_564x234\" src=\"http://localhost/recruitingcms/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/3_564x234-300x124.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"124\" /></a>','精彩活动','','inherit','closed','open','','13-revision-v1','','','2013-09-12 02:04:38','2013-09-12 02:04:38','',13,'http://192.168.222.119/recruitingcms/13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
 (177,1,'2013-09-12 05:26:22','2013-09-12 05:26:22','<!-- understand the augmentum page start -->\r\n        <div id=\'aug-box\'>\r\n            <ul id=\'under_augmentum\'>\r\n                <li>\r\n                    <h1 id=\'domh1\'>群硕介绍</h1>\r\n                    <div class=\'intro content-wrap\'>\r\n                        <p>\r\n                            <img src=\'../wp-content/uploads/2013/08/logo.png\' />\r\n                        <p>\r\n                        <p>\r\n                        群硕软件成立于2003年5月，美国总部位于加州的Foster City，中国总部位于上海，并在武汉和扬州设有研发中心。目前，公司在全球拥有1,000多名员工。\r\n                        </p>\r\n                        <p>群硕软件致力于为全球客户提供基于云上的移动互联网解决方案服务。我们的客户群和业务涉及高科技、公共安全、物流与运输、在线游戏及娱乐、新媒体及电子商务、教育、医疗、绿色能源等领域。</p>\r\n                        <p>通过使用业界领先的开发工具和技术，以及经实践证明被广泛认可的开发流程，群硕团队为国内外客户成功交付了多个软件产品及解决方案，并在移动应用、智能设备、社交网络、社交游戏、云计算、企业系统集成等前沿技术和行业知识方面累积了丰富经验。未来，群硕软件凭借多年来商业级软件产品的开发经验和创新能力，将持续为各行业企业和用户提供下一代变革性产品及解决方案。</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>\r\n                    <h1>企业文化</h1>\r\n                    <div class=\'culture content-wrap\'>\r\n                        <h2>愿景</h2>\r\n                        <p>从成立的第一天起，群硕就确定了清晰的愿景目标。对我们的愿景，我们坚定而执着： </p>\r\n                        <div class=\'banner\'><img src=\'../wp-content/uploads/images/culture_top.png\' /></div>\r\n                        <ol class=\'hope\'>\r\n                            <li><span></span>成为全球顶尖的软件开发服务提供商</li>\r\n                            <li><span></span>在中国建立和培养世界级的软件研发团队</li>\r\n                            <li><span></span>激发每位员工的最大潜能</li>\r\n                            <li><span></span>为中国走在世界软件研发领域的前列有所贡献</li>\r\n                        </ol>\r\n                        <div class=\'banner\'><img src=\'../wp-content/uploads/images/culture_down.png\' /></div>\r\n                        <!---->\r\n                        <h2>核心文化</h2>\r\n                        <p>激情、自律、创新、专注、一致、坚持（Passion, Self-discipline, Creativity, Focus, Consistency and Persistence）</p>\r\n                        <div class=\'banner\'><img src=\'../wp-content/uploads/images/culture2_top.png\' /></div>\r\n                        <ol class=\'core-culture\'>\r\n                            <li><span></span>以客户和市场为导向（Customer / market oriented）</li>\r\n                            <li><span></span>以身作则（Lead by example）</li>\r\n                            <li><span></span>十年树木，百年树人（Experience takes time to accumulate）</li>\r\n                        </ol>\r\n                        <div class=\'banner\'><img src=\'../wp-content/uploads/images/culture2_down.png\' /></div>\r\n                        <!---->\r\n                        <h2>核心价值观</h2>\r\n                        <ol class=\'core-value\'>\r\n                            <li>Win–Win</li>\r\n                            <li>Change With Speed</li>\r\n                            <li>Trust & Commitment</li>\r\n                            <li>Integrity & Ethics</li>\r\n                            <li>Think Out Of Box</li>\r\n                            <li>High Quality</li>\r\n                        </ol>\r\n                        <!---->\r\n                        <ol class=\'detail\'>\r\n                            <li class=\'l\'></li>\r\n                            <li class=\'m\'>诚信与道德 Integrity & Ethics</li>\r\n                            <li class=\'r\'></li>\r\n                        </ol>\r\n                        <p class=\'detail-p\'>诚信与道德是群硕立足并取得成绩的基石，使我们能够提供优质的产品与服务，与客户和合作伙伴建立互信的关系，并在竞争中不断取胜。同时，也是群硕员工团结一致的基础。</p>\r\n                        <ol class=\'detail\'>\r\n                            <li class=\'l\'></li>\r\n                            <li class=\'m\'>信任与承诺 Trust & Commitment</li>\r\n                            <li class=\'r\'></li>\r\n                        </ol>\r\n                        <p class=\'detail-p\'>信任与承诺是群硕员工为人处事的基本原则。信任不能够轻易获得，需要通过长期地、不断地履行承诺来赢得他人的信任。我们强调要尽我们最大的努力传递和履行我们的承诺。</p>\r\n                        <ol class=\'detail\'>\r\n                            <li class=\'l\'></li>\r\n                            <li class=\'m\'>双赢 Win–Win</li>\r\n                            <li class=\'r\'></li>\r\n                        </ol>\r\n                        <p class=\'detail-p\'>在群硕，双赢是我们做任何事情时所追求的目标，我们时刻铭记“只有客户成功，我们才能成功”，“只有员工得到发展，公司才能发展”。双赢并非只是一起分享荣誉或利益，而是在任何时刻我们都能够从对方的角度去思考问题，寻求共同发展。</p>\r\n                        <ol class=\'detail\'>\r\n                            <li class=\'l\'></li>\r\n                            <li class=\'m\'>高品质 High Quality</li>\r\n                            <li class=\'r\'></li>\r\n                        </ol>\r\n                        <p class=\'detail-p\'>作为专业提供软件开发服务的公司，我们非常注重我们所提供产品和服务的质量。我们追求高品质，并非指绝对不犯错误，而是指我们总是设定一个比我们能够做到的程度更高的目标，并努力追求；同时，我们认为追求高品质应该成为我们每个人生活的哲学。</p>\r\n                        <ol class=\'detail\'>\r\n                            <li class=\'l\'></li>\r\n                            <li class=\'m\'>快速改变 Change With Speed</li>\r\n                            <li class=\'r\'></li>\r\n                        </ol>\r\n                        <p class=\'detail-p\'>世界在快速地变化，市场在快速地变化，客户的需求也在快速地变化，我们要在快速变化的环境中寻求发展，我们需要具备快速应对变化的意识和技能，不可因循守旧、固步自封。</p>\r\n                        <ol class=\'detail\'>\r\n                            <li class=\'l\'></li>\r\n                            <li class=\'m\'>开放性思维 Think Out Of Box</li>\r\n                            <li class=\'r\'></li>\r\n                        </ol>\r\n                        <p class=\'detail-p\'>只有打破自我思维的局限，才能更客观、更全面地看待问题。我们希望我们的员工具备开放性的思维，不断创新、开拓，海纳百川。</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>\r\n                    <h1>培训发展</h1>\r\n                    <div class=\'develop content-wrap\'>\r\n                        <h2>持续的多元化培训</h2>\r\n                        <div class=\'dev-top\'></div>\r\n                        <div class=\'dev-mode\'>\r\n                            <div class=\'dev-mode-left\'>\r\n                                <img src=\'../wp-content/uploads/images/ico_dna.png\' />\r\n                                <lable>公司DNA</lable>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <ol class=\'dev-mode-right\'>\r\n                                <li><span></span>公司文化及战略</li>\r\n                                <li><span></span>公司文化及战略</li>\r\n                            </ol>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <!---->\r\n                        <div class=\'dev-hr\'></div>\r\n                        <div class=\'dev-mode dev-mode-skill\'>\r\n                            <div class=\'dev-mode-left\'>\r\n                                <img src=\'../wp-content/uploads/images/ico_skill.png\' />\r\n                                <lable>职业技能培训</lable>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <ol class=\'dev-mode-right\'>\r\n                                <li><span></span>应届生/实习生岗前培训</li>\r\n                                <li><span></span>开发流程和方法</li>\r\n                                <li><span></span>通用技能培训</li>\r\n                                <li><span></span>软件质量管理</li>\r\n                                <li><span></span>项目技能培训</li>\r\n                                <li><span></span>经验知识分享</li>\r\n                            </ol>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <!---->\r\n                        <div class=\'dev-hr\'></div>\r\n                        <div class=\'dev-mode dev-mode-manager\'>\r\n                            <div class=\'dev-mode-left\'>\r\n                                <img src=\'../wp-content/uploads/images/ico_manager.png\' />\r\n                                <lable>管理培训</lable>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <ol class=\'dev-mode-right\'>\r\n                                <li><span></span>项目管理</li>\r\n                                <li><span></span>团队管理</li>\r\n                                <li><span></span>客户管理</li>\r\n                                <li><span></span>领导力培训</li>\r\n                            </ol>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <!---->\r\n                        <div class=\'dev-hr\'></div>\r\n                        <div class=\'dev-mode dev-mode-english\'>\r\n                            <div class=\'dev-mode-left\'>\r\n                                <img src=\'../wp-content/uploads/images/ico_english.png\' />\r\n                                <lable>管理培训</lable>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <ol class=\'dev-mode-right\'>\r\n                                <li><span></span>基础英语培训</li>\r\n                                <li><span></span>“一对一”英语培训</li>\r\n                                <li><span></span>英文工作环境</li>\r\n                            </ol>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\'dev-foot\'></div>\r\n                        <div class=\'dev-hr\'></div>\r\n                        <div class=\'dev-hr\'></div>\r\n                        <div class=\'dev-hr\'></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>\r\n                    <h1>薪酬福利</h1>\r\n                    <div class=\'salary content-wrap\'>\r\n                        <ol>\r\n                            <li><span></span>具有竞争力的薪资水平</li>\r\n                            <li><span></span>基于工作绩效的年度加薪机制</li>\r\n                            <li><span></span>年度服务奖金：年度服务奖金标准为一个月的固定工资</li>\r\n                            <li><span></span>符合国家规定的社会保险和住房公积金</li>\r\n                            <li><span></span>带薪年假、法定节假日、及各种带薪假期</li>\r\n                            <li><span></span>生日礼品、女生节礼包、中秋节礼物、端午节礼物</li>\r\n                            <li><span></span>年度健康体检与健康咨询</li>\r\n                            <li><span></span>海外差旅保险、员工异地工作补贴</li>\r\n                            <li><span></span>公司新年晚会、家庭活动日、篮球赛、新员工拓展活动等</li>\r\n                            <li><span></span>解决符合条件的户口、居住证</li>\r\n                        </ol>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\'dev-hr\'></div>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>\r\n                    <h1>工作环境</h1>\r\n                    <div class=\'rim content-wrap\'>\r\n                        <h2>办公环境</h2>\r\n                        <h2>周边生活环境</h2>\r\n                        <div class=\'dev-hr\'></div>\r\n                        <dl>\r\n                            <dt>上海</dt>\r\n                            <dd><span></span>交通</dd>\r\n                            <dd><span></span>住房</dd>\r\n                            <dd><span></span>娱乐</dd>\r\n                            <dd><span></span>餐饮</dd>\r\n                        </dl>\r\n                        <div class=\'dev-hr\'></div>\r\n                        <dl>\r\n                            <dt>武汉</dt>\r\n                            <dd><span></span>交通</dd>\r\n                            <dd><span></span>住房</dd>\r\n                            <dd><span></span>娱乐</dd>\r\n                            <dd><span></span>餐饮</dd>\r\n                        </dl>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <!-- understand the augmentum page end -->','认识群硕','','inherit','closed','open','','22-revision-v1','','','2013-09-12 05:26:22','2013-09-12 05:26:22','',22,'http://192.168.222.119/recruitingcms/22-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
