 (306,1,'2014-01-27 02:24:40','2014-01-27 02:24:40','<div class=\"question-content\">\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q1</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕是什么性质的公司？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕是一家外商独资企业。群硕美国总部位于加州的Foster City，中国总部位于上海，并在武汉和扬州设有分公司。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕的业务领域？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕软件致力于为全球客户提供基于云上的移动互联网解决方案服务。我们的客户群和业务涉及高科技、公共安全、物流与运输、在线游戏及娱乐、新媒体及电子商务、教育、医疗、绿色能源等领域，并在移动应用、智能设备、社交网络、社交游戏、云计算、企业系统集成等前沿技术和行业知识方面累积了丰富经验。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>什么是应届生招聘？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>通常情况下，公司每年会通过高校招募应届同学。通过面试的同学，公司会直接与同学们签订《聘雇协议》（offer letter）和三方协议。报到之后，应届同学会接受专业技能、职业发展、职业素养、公司文化等系列入职培训。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>什么是实习生招聘？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>公司欢迎符合条件的同学提前到公司实习。经过实习面试的同学，公司先与其签订《实习协议》。实习期间，实习同学可享有全面的专业技能基础实训、实习津贴、商业医疗保险和意外保险、团队活动等。当公司和实习同学都有意愿长期合作时，公司会与同学们签订《聘雇协议》（offer letter）和三方协议，实习同学毕业后即成为公司正式员工。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>什么是社会招聘？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>根据公司发展和岗位需要，公司会招募社会人才。社会人才报到当日，公司即会与其签订《劳动合同》。公司的项目技术环境、平等友好的工作环境、积极向上的工作氛围，一定可以帮助社会人才尽快融入环境，开启一段持续发展的职业道路。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>具体的工作地点可能在哪里？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕在上海、武汉都设有工作岗位。详见招聘职位。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕一定只录用校园宣讲所覆盖的高校或者地区的学生吗？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕在人才招聘方面一直强调不拘一格降人才。因此，对于校园招聘， 我们虽然选取了一些地区开展校园招聘活动，但只要您是优秀的人才，并符合我们的用人标准，我们都非常欢迎您加盟群硕。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>通过什么途径可以了解群硕的校园招聘行程安排及进展情况？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>可以通过大街群硕主页、群硕微信详细了解相关信息。同时，我们也会在学校就业网站上及时发布最新进展情况。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>校园招聘的具体流程是怎样的？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>首先会通过各种渠道将群硕软件的招聘信息告诉同学们，然后会通知同学们前来笔试。接下来我们会邀请笔试合格者接受我们两轮及以上的面试，从中我们会确定合适的人选并发放录用通知。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>校园宣讲会现场是否接收简历申请？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>为了保证同学们的简历信息能够被完整地录入到我们的人才信息系统中，对于在宣讲会之前未来得及投递简历的同学，我们仍然建议同学们在宣讲会后尽快登录大街投递简历。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>公司有针对学生的培训项目吗？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕十分重视员工的培训与发展。目前，针对应届和实习同学的培训体系已经有效运行多年。通过该培训，同学们能够掌握基础专业技能，培养良好的工作规范和工作习惯，并在英语运用能力方面有较大提高。在培训期间，公司将安排技术经理、授课讲师、导师全程提供指导和帮助。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>如果申请中被拒，是否有相关通知，大概是多长时间通知？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>由于每年校园招聘申请人数众多，我们会优先在第一时间公布通过每轮甄选的同学名单。对于未能通过甄选的同学，我们暂时不能保证会第一时间知会到每一位同学，请大家谅解。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>应届生对最终的工作城市是否有自主选择权，还是需要服从公司调剂？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>原则上，公司根据实际业务需求以及岗位本身，对同学们工作地做出安排。同时，从人性化的角度出发，在综合考虑到同学们学校所在地、公司实际业务需求、同学们的个人需求等因素，尽力满足同学们对具体工作城市的选择。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>对于应届生，Offer Letter、三方协议、正式劳动合同分别在什么时候签？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>被正式录取后，公司会与同学们签订Offer Letter、三方协议。当同学们毕业报到第一天，公司会与员工签订正式劳动合同。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕员工职业发展道路是怎么样的？ </span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕员工职业发展道路分二个主要方向：专业技术方向和管理方向，二个方向都有广阔的发展空间。结合员工个人职业倾向性、工作绩效、工作能力，公司会提供适合的发展机会和培养计划。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕的薪资体系是什么？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕坚持公平透明的竞争机制，坚持有效的绩效考评机制与激励型的薪酬体系，以此，推动员工持续发展并创造高工作绩效。群硕每年会结合企业实际，制定出既有外部竞争力又符合群硕的薪酬激励体制。通过过去几年激励机制和培养计划的有效运行，已证明群硕为优秀员工的快速成长提供了支持平台，并在薪酬方面提供了充分的激励性。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕的福利待遇如何？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕为员工提供完善的福利，其中包括：符合国家规定的社会保险、住房公积金、年度服务奖金、年度健康体检、带薪年假、法定节假日及各种带薪假期、生日祝福和生日礼品、节日礼品、异地工作员工合理补贴、员工年度活动经费、大型公司活动、团队活动资金支持等。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"notice\"><span>大家如果还有更多的疑问，欢迎通过大街-“群硕软件公司”招聘主页或“群硕招聘”微信平台提出问题，我们将尽快给予回复。再次感谢大家对群硕的关注和支持。</span></div>\r\n</div>','Q&A','','inherit','closed','open','','37-revision-v1','','','2014-01-27 02:24:40','2014-01-27 02:24:40','',37,'http://192.168.222.177:8011//37-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
 (305,1,'2014-01-27 02:23:50','2014-01-27 02:23:50','<div class=\"question-content\">\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>Q1：群硕是什么性质的公司？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕是一家外商独资企业。群硕美国总部位于加州的Foster City，中国总部位于上海，并在武汉和扬州设有分公司。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕的业务领域？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕软件致力于为全球客户提供基于云上的移动互联网解决方案服务。我们的客户群和业务涉及高科技、公共安全、物流与运输、在线游戏及娱乐、新媒体及电子商务、教育、医疗、绿色能源等领域，并在移动应用、智能设备、社交网络、社交游戏、云计算、企业系统集成等前沿技术和行业知识方面累积了丰富经验。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>什么是应届生招聘？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>通常情况下，公司每年会通过高校招募应届同学。通过面试的同学，公司会直接与同学们签订《聘雇协议》（offer letter）和三方协议。报到之后，应届同学会接受专业技能、职业发展、职业素养、公司文化等系列入职培训。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>什么是实习生招聘？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>公司欢迎符合条件的同学提前到公司实习。经过实习面试的同学，公司先与其签订《实习协议》。实习期间，实习同学可享有全面的专业技能基础实训、实习津贴、商业医疗保险和意外保险、团队活动等。当公司和实习同学都有意愿长期合作时，公司会与同学们签订《聘雇协议》（offer letter）和三方协议，实习同学毕业后即成为公司正式员工。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>什么是社会招聘？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>根据公司发展和岗位需要，公司会招募社会人才。社会人才报到当日，公司即会与其签订《劳动合同》。公司的项目技术环境、平等友好的工作环境、积极向上的工作氛围，一定可以帮助社会人才尽快融入环境，开启一段持续发展的职业道路。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>具体的工作地点可能在哪里？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕在上海、武汉都设有工作岗位。详见招聘职位。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕一定只录用校园宣讲所覆盖的高校或者地区的学生吗？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕在人才招聘方面一直强调不拘一格降人才。因此，对于校园招聘， 我们虽然选取了一些地区开展校园招聘活动，但只要您是优秀的人才，并符合我们的用人标准，我们都非常欢迎您加盟群硕。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>通过什么途径可以了解群硕的校园招聘行程安排及进展情况？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>可以通过大街群硕主页、群硕微信详细了解相关信息。同时，我们也会在学校就业网站上及时发布最新进展情况。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>校园招聘的具体流程是怎样的？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>首先会通过各种渠道将群硕软件的招聘信息告诉同学们，然后会通知同学们前来笔试。接下来我们会邀请笔试合格者接受我们两轮及以上的面试，从中我们会确定合适的人选并发放录用通知。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>校园宣讲会现场是否接收简历申请？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>为了保证同学们的简历信息能够被完整地录入到我们的人才信息系统中，对于在宣讲会之前未来得及投递简历的同学，我们仍然建议同学们在宣讲会后尽快登录大街投递简历。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>公司有针对学生的培训项目吗？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕十分重视员工的培训与发展。目前，针对应届和实习同学的培训体系已经有效运行多年。通过该培训，同学们能够掌握基础专业技能，培养良好的工作规范和工作习惯，并在英语运用能力方面有较大提高。在培训期间，公司将安排技术经理、授课讲师、导师全程提供指导和帮助。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>如果申请中被拒，是否有相关通知，大概是多长时间通知？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>由于每年校园招聘申请人数众多，我们会优先在第一时间公布通过每轮甄选的同学名单。对于未能通过甄选的同学，我们暂时不能保证会第一时间知会到每一位同学，请大家谅解。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>应届生对最终的工作城市是否有自主选择权，还是需要服从公司调剂？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>原则上，公司根据实际业务需求以及岗位本身，对同学们工作地做出安排。同时，从人性化的角度出发，在综合考虑到同学们学校所在地、公司实际业务需求、同学们的个人需求等因素，尽力满足同学们对具体工作城市的选择。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>对于应届生，Offer Letter、三方协议、正式劳动合同分别在什么时候签？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>被正式录取后，公司会与同学们签订Offer Letter、三方协议。当同学们毕业报到第一天，公司会与员工签订正式劳动合同。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕员工职业发展道路是怎么样的？ </span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕员工职业发展道路分二个主要方向：专业技术方向和管理方向，二个方向都有广阔的发展空间。结合员工个人职业倾向性、工作绩效、工作能力，公司会提供适合的发展机会和培养计划。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕的薪资体系是什么？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕坚持公平透明的竞争机制，坚持有效的绩效考评机制与激励型的薪酬体系，以此，推动员工持续发展并创造高工作绩效。群硕每年会结合企业实际，制定出既有外部竞争力又符合群硕的薪酬激励体制。通过过去几年激励机制和培养计划的有效运行，已证明群硕为优秀员工的快速成长提供了支持平台，并在薪酬方面提供了充分的激励性。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕的福利待遇如何？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕为员工提供完善的福利，其中包括：符合国家规定的社会保险、住房公积金、年度服务奖金、年度健康体检、带薪年假、法定节假日及各种带薪假期、生日祝福和生日礼品、节日礼品、异地工作员工合理补贴、员工年度活动经费、大型公司活动、团队活动资金支持等。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"notice\"><span>大家如果还有更多的疑问，欢迎通过大街-“群硕软件公司”招聘主页或“群硕招聘”微信平台提出问题，我们将尽快给予回复。再次感谢大家对群硕的关注和支持。</span></div>\r\n</div>','Q&A','','inherit','closed','open','','37-revision-v1','','','2014-01-27 02:23:50','2014-01-27 02:23:50','',37,'http://192.168.222.177:8011//37-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
 (307,1,'2014-01-27 02:28:41','2014-01-27 02:28:41','<div class=\"question-content\">\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q1</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕是什么性质的公司？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕是一家外商独资企业。群硕美国总部位于加州的Foster City，中国总部位于上海，并在武汉和扬州设有分公司。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q2</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕的业务领域？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕软件致力于为全球客户提供基于云上的移动互联网解决方案服务。我们的客户群和业务涉及高科技、公共安全、物流与运输、在线游戏及娱乐、新媒体及电子商务、教育、医疗、绿色能源等领域，并在移动应用、智能设备、社交网络、社交游戏、云计算、企业系统集成等前沿技术和行业知识方面累积了丰富经验。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q3</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>什么是应届生招聘？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>通常情况下，公司每年会通过高校招募应届同学。通过面试的同学，公司会直接与同学们签订《聘雇协议》（offer letter）和三方协议。报到之后，应届同学会接受专业技能、职业发展、职业素养、公司文化等系列入职培训。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q4</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>什么是实习生招聘？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>公司欢迎符合条件的同学提前到公司实习。经过实习面试的同学，公司先与其签订《实习协议》。实习期间，实习同学可享有全面的专业技能基础实训、实习津贴、商业医疗保险和意外保险、团队活动等。当公司和实习同学都有意愿长期合作时，公司会与同学们签订《聘雇协议》（offer letter）和三方协议，实习同学毕业后即成为公司正式员工。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q5</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>什么是社会招聘？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>根据公司发展和岗位需要，公司会招募社会人才。社会人才报到当日，公司即会与其签订《劳动合同》。公司的项目技术环境、平等友好的工作环境、积极向上的工作氛围，一定可以帮助社会人才尽快融入环境，开启一段持续发展的职业道路。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q6</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>具体的工作地点可能在哪里？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕在上海、武汉都设有工作岗位。详见招聘职位。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q7</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕一定只录用校园宣讲所覆盖的高校或者地区的学生吗？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕在人才招聘方面一直强调不拘一格降人才。因此，对于校园招聘， 我们虽然选取了一些地区开展校园招聘活动，但只要您是优秀的人才，并符合我们的用人标准，我们都非常欢迎您加盟群硕。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q8</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>通过什么途径可以了解群硕的校园招聘行程安排及进展情况？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>可以通过大街群硕主页、群硕微信详细了解相关信息。同时，我们也会在学校就业网站上及时发布最新进展情况。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q9</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>校园招聘的具体流程是怎样的？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>首先会通过各种渠道将群硕软件的招聘信息告诉同学们，然后会通知同学们前来笔试。接下来我们会邀请笔试合格者接受我们两轮及以上的面试，从中我们会确定合适的人选并发放录用通知。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q10</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>校园宣讲会现场是否接收简历申请？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>为了保证同学们的简历信息能够被完整地录入到我们的人才信息系统中，对于在宣讲会之前未来得及投递简历的同学，我们仍然建议同学们在宣讲会后尽快登录大街投递简历。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q11</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>公司有针对学生的培训项目吗？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕十分重视员工的培训与发展。目前，针对应届和实习同学的培训体系已经有效运行多年。通过该培训，同学们能够掌握基础专业技能，培养良好的工作规范和工作习惯，并在英语运用能力方面有较大提高。在培训期间，公司将安排技术经理、授课讲师、导师全程提供指导和帮助。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q12</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>如果申请中被拒，是否有相关通知，大概是多长时间通知？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>由于每年校园招聘申请人数众多，我们会优先在第一时间公布通过每轮甄选的同学名单。对于未能通过甄选的同学，我们暂时不能保证会第一时间知会到每一位同学，请大家谅解。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q13</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>应届生对最终的工作城市是否有自主选择权，还是需要服从公司调剂？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>原则上，公司根据实际业务需求以及岗位本身，对同学们工作地做出安排。同时，从人性化的角度出发，在综合考虑到同学们学校所在地、公司实际业务需求、同学们的个人需求等因素，尽力满足同学们对具体工作城市的选择。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q14</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>对于应届生，Offer Letter、三方协议、正式劳动合同分别在什么时候签？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>被正式录取后，公司会与同学们签订Offer Letter、三方协议。当同学们毕业报到第一天，公司会与员工签订正式劳动合同。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q15</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕员工职业发展道路是怎么样的？ </span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕员工职业发展道路分二个主要方向：专业技术方向和管理方向，二个方向都有广阔的发展空间。结合员工个人职业倾向性、工作绩效、工作能力，公司会提供适合的发展机会和培养计划。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q16</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕的薪资体系是什么？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕坚持公平透明的竞争机制，坚持有效的绩效考评机制与激励型的薪酬体系，以此，推动员工持续发展并创造高工作绩效。群硕每年会结合企业实际，制定出既有外部竞争力又符合群硕的薪酬激励体制。通过过去几年激励机制和培养计划的有效运行，已证明群硕为优秀员工的快速成长提供了支持平台，并在薪酬方面提供了充分的激励性。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"question-item\"><span class=\"item-user\">Q17</span>\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕的福利待遇如何？</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"answer-item\">\r\n<div class=\"item-content\">\r\n<div class=\"t_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"t_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_m\"><span>群硕为员工提供完善的福利，其中包括：符合国家规定的社会保险、住房公积金、年度服务奖金、年度健康体检、带薪年假、法定节假日及各种带薪假期、生日祝福和生日礼品、节日礼品、异地工作员工合理补贴、员工年度活动经费、大型公司活动、团队活动资金支持等。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"m_r\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_l\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_m\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"b_r\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"item-user\">A</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"notice\"><span>大家如果还有更多的疑问，欢迎通过大街-“群硕软件公司”招聘主页或“群硕招聘”微信平台提出问题，我们将尽快给予回复。再次感谢大家对群硕的关注和支持。</span></div>\r\n</div>','Q&A','','inherit','closed','open','','37-revision-v1','','','2014-01-27 02:28:41','2014-01-27 02:28:41','',37,'http://192.168.222.177:8011//37-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
